sentences: Kim Jong-dae (born September 21, 1992), better known by his stage name, Chen, is a South Korean singer and songwriter.
He debuted in 2012 as a member of the South Korean-Chinese boy band Exo and its subgroup Exo-M, and has since further participated in SM Entertainment's projects Exo-CBX and SM the Ballad.
